<plot>Chronicles Cleveland Amory's passion for animal rights from his first experience with bullfighting in Mexico to his death in 1998. The film follows his activities in the US and abroad, while sparking a movement and a legacy which lives on. Included are archival footage, photo's and interviews as well as new footage and interviews with Hollywood Celebrities who not only knew but loved, admired and respected this Charasmatic Curmudgeon and author of "The Cat Who Came for Christmas".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?353469</url></doc>
